<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>notes on A'Khun</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/</link><description>Recent content in notes on A'Khun</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://akhun.co/notes/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Facebook</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/facebook/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/notes/facebook/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="demo-facebook-後端登入流程" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#demo-facebook-%e5%be%8c%e7%ab%af%e7%99%bb%e5%85%a5%e6%b5%81%e7%a8%8b">[Demo] Facebook 後端登入流程&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>參考官方文件 &lt;a href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-login/manually-build-a-login-flow/">Manually Build a Login Flow&lt;/a>，用 Python 實作使用者從前端按下登入按鈕，跳出 Facebook Login Dialog 確認授權後，前端再打後端 api，讓後端取得 access token，完成登入流程。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>macOS</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/macos/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/notes/macos/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="關掉單雙引號的自動轉換" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#%e9%97%9c%e6%8e%89%e5%96%ae%e9%9b%99%e5%bc%95%e8%99%9f%e7%9a%84%e8%87%aa%e5%8b%95%e8%bd%89%e6%8f%9b">關掉單、雙引號的自動轉換&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>這一年開始拿 Mac 作為工作機，在使用 Evernote 時常遇到煩人的狀況，就是每當在 Note 輸入雙引號（&amp;quot;），都會被自動換成（“），單引號（&amp;rsquo;）會被換成（‘）。因為常用的 bash command 會存在 Evernote 裡面，每次從 Evernote 剪下貼到 Terminal 的時候都會執行錯誤，實在覺得&lt;del>很靠北&lt;/del>非常惱人。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>virtualenvwrapper</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/virtualenvwrapper/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/notes/virtualenvwrapper/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="install" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#install">Install&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>pip install virtualenvwrapper
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="environment-bashrc" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#environment-bashrc">Environment (.bashrc)&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># virtualenvwrapper&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export WORKON_HOME&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>$HOME/.virtualenvs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export PROJECT_HOME&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>$HOME/works
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>source /usr/local/bin/virtualenvwrapper.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="basic-commands" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#basic-commands">Basic commands&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
