&lt;h3 id="corequotepath" class="anchor-link">&lt;a href="#corequotepath">core.quotePath&lt;span class="pilcrow">&amp;nbsp;¶&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>解決 unicode 檔名在 macOS 亂碼的問題。舉例來說，在某個 git repo，如果有個 unicode 檔名的檔案：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>touch 測試.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>把 &lt;code>quotePath&lt;/code> 設成 &lt;code>true&lt;/code>（預設），會看到亂碼：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&amp;gt; git config --global core.quotePath true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&amp;gt; git status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Untracked files:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>use &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;git add &amp;lt;file&amp;gt;...&amp;#34;&lt;/span> to include in what will be committed&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>	&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;\346\270\254\350\251\246.md&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>把 &lt;code>quotePath&lt;/code> 設成 &lt;code>false&lt;/code>，就能正常顯示：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Homebrew</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/homebrew/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/notes/homebrew/</guid><description/></item><item><title>How to fall asleep</title><link>https://akhun.co/notes/how-to-fall-asleep/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/notes/how-to-fall-asleep/</guid><description>&lt;ul>
